	"description": "Micro-frontends are the future of front end web development.\n\nInspired by microservices, which allow you to break up your backend into smaller\npieces, micro-frontends allow you to build, test, and deploy pieces of your\nfrontend app independently of each other. \n\nDepending on the micro-frontend framework you choose, you can even have multiple\nmicro-frontend apps — written in React, Angular, Vue, or anything else —\ncoexisting peacefully together in the same larger app.\n\nIn this article, we’re goin",
